           <p class="font_8" style="font-size:13px; line-height:1.2em;">
            <span style="font-size:13px;">
             <span class="color_16">
              CRM Science is a strategic salesforce consulting and development practice focused on quality delivery and customer success. CRM Science won the 2016 and 2017 Salesforce Partner Innovation Award for enterprise development and implementation and is also an official Salesforce Product Development Outsourcing (PDO) company, which is awarded to Salesforce consulting partners with excellent development resources and track record.
             </span>
            </span>
           </p>
           <p class="font_8" style="font-size:13px; line-height:1.2em;">
           </p>
           <p class="font_8" style="font-size:13px; line-height:1.2em;">
            <span style="font-size:13px;">
             <span class="color_16">
              We build internal business processes, integrate external solutions, and clean messy orgs. Our consultants' architect, design, develop and implement solutions tailored specifically to your business needs in order to ensure you achieve your goals.
             </span>
            </span>
           </p>
           <p class="font_8" style="font-size:13px; line-height:1.2em;">
           </p>

            <span style="font-size:13px;">
             <span class="color_16">
              Our goal at CRM Science is to provide effective solutions designed to boost your business.
             </span>
            </span>
           </p>
